Class CookieBufferingFilter.CookieBufferingHttpServletResponseProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.ServletResponseWrapper
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponseWrapper

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse, javax.servlet.ServletResponse
    Enclosing class:
    CookieBufferingFilter

    private class CookieBufferingFilter.CookieBufferingHttpServletResponseProxy
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponseWrapper
    An implementation of HttpServletResponse which buffers added cookies to ensure only a single cookie of a given name is eventually set.
